# A "multilines" answer

Widget 40
Property
    Flags NoReliefString
    Position 30 140
    Size 150 20
    Type PushButton
    Title {A "Multilines" Msg}
Main
Case message of
 SingleClic :
 Begin
    Set $tmp = (SendMsgAndGet $ComName {multilines} 1)
    Set $t1 = (Parse $tmp 1)
    Set $t2 = (Parse $tmp 2)
    Set $t3 = (Parse $tmp 3)
    ChangeTitle 41 $t1
    ChangeTitle 42 $t2
    ChangeTitle 43 $t3
  End
End

