Widget 99
Property
    Size 80 20
    Position 250 250
    Flags NoReliefString
    Type PushButton
    Title {Quit}
Main
Case message of
 SingleClic :
 Begin
    # say to fvwm-script-ComExample.pl to exit the 0 says that we do not
    # need an answer
    Set $dummy = (SendMsgAndGet $ComName {exit} 0)
    Quit
 End
